{"tid":1912012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實話放棄立法會果啲人諗緊乜","createTime":"2020-03-05T18:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T20:32:57.000Z","uid":126865,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"70aab57c0810e5be9f316a3be914f1bb034fb505","tid":1912012,"uid":126865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:16:16.000Z","msg":"全力爭取立法會過半=&gt;體制外繼續抗爭<br />\n放棄立法會=&gt;體制外繼續抗爭<br />\n<br />\n講到玩立法會就唔可以抗爭咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n立法會係唔可以達到真普選但係都係一種手段<br />\n<br />\n玩立法會同放棄比，邊樣會先係會令我地距離五大訴求近啲？<br />\n<br />\nPs. 話玩立法會美國就唔會幫我地果啲其實明唔明國際政治上，如果美國見到利益話之你立法會放唔放棄，佢點都會幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4747b78ff4a84caab15589fd2329be864d9bf1","tid":1912012,"uid":313072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:18:14.000Z","msg":"立會係點都要選嘅"},{"pid":"920758298a62dcc0f77e170104c5bd3918e7da15","tid":1912012,"uid":126865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:20:37.000Z","msg":"話選舉冇用嘅人入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c4115003399ebc26b2fb5ec08b515bc690ef40c4","tid":1912012,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:23:29.000Z","msg":"議會戰線不能放棄<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"159af174840407be6410cc1e58bb319c74ba030e","tid":1912012,"uid":128603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:23:58.000Z","msg":"親共派知你唔會投佢，所以派人叫你放棄。<br />\n<br />\n你都可以同藍屍講，高投票率會被解讀為對政府不滿，小心中計。"},{"pid":"98f7d6df4132b7d55d57b9d6bfabc4db83737f64","tid":1912012,"uid":126865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"真心唔明，叫人放棄果啲其實係鬼定係真心豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175f7108402ca1309fccbf034ce79cec2ef36cd9","tid":1912012,"uid":313072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"98f7d6df4132b7d55d57b9d6bfabc4db83737f64","tid":1912012,"uid":126865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"真心唔明，叫人放棄果啲其實係鬼定係真心豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:29:45.000Z","msg":"我覺得似鬼"},{"pid":"d896983881d30eaa079b8c597cc9cd43936df2ff","tid":1912012,"uid":126865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"175f7108402ca1309fccbf034ce79cec2ef36cd9","tid":1912012,"uid":313072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"98f7d6df4132b7d55d57b9d6bfabc4db83737f64","tid":1912012,"uid":126865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"真心唔明，叫人放棄果啲其實係鬼定係真心豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:29:45.000Z","msg":"我覺得似鬼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T18:37:49.000Z","msg":"啲風向帶到咁<img src=\"/assets